  For more information about the test utilities, visit:
  
    http://software.sandia.gov/trilinos/developer/test_harness/
    
  or run the following for the utility you're interested in:
  
    perl runbuild --help
    perl runconfigure --help
    perl runmake --help
    perl runtests --help
    perl report --help